8" rel="nofollow">Other <span class="qty">(20)</span> </a></li><li class="chkFacet"><a href="/Search/Crime/Books/eBook/Map?fq=121800-01120-1147-1146" rel="nofollow">Map <span class="qty">(2)</span> </a></li><li class="chkFacet"><a href="/Search/Crime/Books/eBook/Mixed-Media?fq=121800-01120-1147-1145" rel="nofollow">Mixed Media <span class="qty">(1)</span> </a></li></ul></div><div class="refineItem"><h5>Price</h5><ul class="facetDetailList  withCheckboxes"><li class="chkFacet"><a href="/Search/Crime/Books/eBook/£5-to-£10?fq=121800-01120-1147-022" rel="nofollow">£5 to £10 <span class="qty">(2)</span> </a></li><li class="chkFacet"><a href="/Search/Crime/Books/eBook/£10-to-£20?fq=121800-01120-1147-023" rel="nofollow">£10 to £20 <span class="qty">(1)</span> </a></li></ul></div><div class="refineItem"><h5>Author</h5><ul class="facetDetailList  withCheckboxes"><li class="chkFacet"><a href="/Search/Crime/Books/eBook/Jeff-Dixon?fq=121800-01120-1147-132785220" rel="nofollow">Jeff Dixon <span class="qty">(1)</span> </a></li><li class="chkFacet"><a href="/Search/Crime/Books/eBook/Toni-Kan?fq=121800-01120-1147-135917706" rel="nofollow">Toni Kan <span class="qty">(1)</span> </a></li><li class="chkFacet"><a href="/Search/Crime/Books/eBook/JESPER-STEIN?fq=121800-01120-1147-136588732" rel="nofollow">JESPER STEIN <span class="qty">(1)</span> </a></li></ul></div></div></div></div>

